- 'garden of tags' represents the 'benchmark_tags' table;
- 'names' correspond to the 'tag' column;
- 'scent of their descriptions' corresponds to the 'description' column.

- Specific user refers to user_id = 1;
- Certain visualization refers to visualization_id = 1;
- Identifiers of performance metrics refer to result_id;
- Labels of the performance metrics refer to tag.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT uv.user_id) AS unique_owner_count
FROM visualization_users uv
WHERE uv.role = 'owner';
